nodes.text: Vineau was a male Human who served in the Republic Army during the Galactic War with the reconstituted Sith Empire. During the Quesh war on the planet Quesh, he was stationed at the Republic Operational Headquarters.

Vineau appeared in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as a Modification Commendations Vendor for Republic players on Quesh. With the release of Game Update 4.0 on October 20, 2015, Vineau was removed from the game along with the rest of the Modification Commendations Vendors. His position is also marked on a map in Star Wars: The Old Republic Explorer's Guide, a game guide released by Prima Games.
